
# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.2.0] - 2025-04-18

### Added
- Iconography page now displays a sample grid of Lucide icons with preview, search, and click-to-copy import statement functionality.
- Improved Iconography page title and subtitle styling to match Foundation page.

### Fixed
- Bug: Lucide icons now imported via explicit named imports to ensure compatibility with Vite/ESM; wildcard import is no longer used.

## [0.1.0] - 2023-11-28

